cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI

The paper proposes an end-to-end solution for jointly reconstructing room layout, object bounding boxes, and meshes from a single image, which involves computer vision (CV) and robotics (RO) techniques. The method also utilizes graph representations (GR) and machine learning (ML) algorithms for scene understanding and object reconstruction. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.LG, and cs.AI.
